WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.643 --> 00:00:02.976
Of the criteria just mentioned,

2
00:00:02.976 --> 00:00:05.780
data accuracy is the most critical.

3
00:00:05.780 --> 00:00:08.757
Data accuracy counts for all business actions

4
00:00:08.757 --> 00:00:10.835
and inventory control.

5
00:00:10.835 --> 00:00:13.056
In order for data to be accurate,

6
00:00:13.056 --> 00:00:15.998
two important actions have to take place.

7
00:00:15.998 --> 00:00:19.106
First, the right values have to be entered,

8
00:00:19.106 --> 00:00:21.548
such as pricing and the number of items.

9
00:00:21.548 --> 00:00:24.524
Second, the data always has to be precise

10
00:00:24.524 --> 00:00:27.355
when input into the inventory system.

11
00:00:27.355 --> 00:00:30.030
Always enter information such as vendors,

12
00:00:30.030 --> 00:00:33.176
packaging, and details accurately and correctly.

